# Visual Rules

Follow `docs/DESIGN.md` for all styling decisions.

# Tokens

Use Tailwind theme tokens, not hardcoded hex in components:

- `bg-background`, `text-text`, `text-text-muted`
- `text-accent-cyan`, `text-accent-purple`, `border-accent-cyan/30`

# Components

- Glass cards: `bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-xl`
- Primary button: gradient `from-accent-cyan to-accent-purple`
- Max hover scale: `1.02` via Framer Motion

# Motion

- Use Framer Motion for scroll fade-in and stagger
- Check `prefers-reduced-motion` and skip animations when set
- No infinite distracting loops on primary content

# Accessibility

- WCAG AA contrast on body text
- `aria-label` on icon-only links
- Visible focus rings: `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent-cyan/50`
